translation.Name: Buak_Note_49
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_2: So a few years back, this guy strolls into the shop, and I coulda sworn he was famous. Looked just like Little Lad, the big-shot musician!
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_3: Turns out, it was just some dude named Todd somethin'.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_4: Didn't think much of it till bam, he went missin' just a few weeks later!
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_5: Thought that was the end of it, but then recently, Little Lad himself goes missin' too! Coincidence? I reckon not!
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_6: I coulda sworn I seen that Todd fella in the woods a few days ago... I wonder whatâ€™s goin' on with 'em and if they ARE secretly Little Lad!
